  "title": "Purchaser",
  "description": "<ul><li>Responsible to source, negotiate and purchase Construction Materials, Machineries & Equipments from both local and oversea vendors.</li><li>Maintain up to date prices from suppliers.</li><li>Liaise and follow up with suppliers / vendors.</li><li>Raising invoice/debit note where applicable.</li><li>Responsible for raising/typing purchase requisition and purchase order.</li><li>Perform other ad-hoc duties as assigned from Department Head.</li><li>Make sure correct items quoted & match with site requirement.</li><li>Prepare relevant reports for purchasing.</li><li>Assist in ISO audit documentation.</li></ul><p>For interested applicants, please apply online or send your resume in WORD format to <strong>davidnhbsg@gmail.com; ram@deshingroup.com; wayne@deshingroup.com; shawn@deshingroup.com</strong></p><p>Thank you for your application but we regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</p>",
